</tr>
<tr style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: left;\">
<td style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: left; vertical-align: text-top; padding: 5px 15px 5px 5px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170);\">string</td>
<td style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: left; vertical-align: text-top; padding: 5px 15px 5px 5px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170);\">必需。规定要检查的字符串。</td>
</tr>
<tr style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: left;\">
<td style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: left; vertical-align: text-top; padding: 5px 15px 5px 5px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170);\">length</td>
